product_name: Gateway Chromebook, 15.6" HD, Intel Pentium N6000, Quad Core, 4GB RAM, 128GB Storage, 1MP Webcam, Chrome OS, Black, GCNP41524-BK
short_description:
Check out more Gateway Products at Walmart.com/Gateway

Introducing the New Gateway 15.6" Chromebook

Our new 15.6” Chromebook from Gateway is the ultimate portable notebook that brings crystal-clear picture for all of your tasks and an extravagant new design. You’re guaranteed to experience clarity with a 15.6” LCD HD Display and precision touchpad. The computer is powered by an Intel Pentium Silver Processor and has 4 GB memory RAM.

Chromebook. Ready when you are.

Chromebook boots up as fast as six seconds,* so it’s ready when you are. No more waiting when you have something really important to do. Whether you’re working in a meeting or taking notes in class, just open up your Chromebook and get going. With automatic software updates every six weeks, your device gets the latest software without interrupting you. Google Assistant on Chromebook** also helps you multitask and get things done quickly. Thanks to Launcher on Chromebook, you can search Google, your Drive, your apps, local files and more – all from one place. Search in one spot, get things done faster.

*Boot up speed varies depending on device.

** An Internet connection is required to enable Google Assistant.

Chromebook. Upgrade to easy.

Simplify life with a Chromebook. Just start by logging in to your Google Account and you’ll be off and running. Even if you’re not connected to Wi-Fi, you can keep getting things done when you’re offline.* Get all the apps you love from the Google Play Store. And with up to 10 hours of battery life**, you don’t even need to remember your charger.

*A user needs to enable offline access in different apps to take full advantage of Chromebook’s offline capabilities.

**Battery life may vary based on device and upon usage and other conditions.
